---
title: Mexican Beef, Mushroom & Kidney Bean Pie with Cucumber Salad & Filo Pastry
description: When you fuse beans and pastry you get this amazing red kidney bean filo pastry pie. There’s veggies packed in and cooked through a fiery tomato sauce to make a filling that will make your mouth water. It’s a perfect combination!
